당신에게 바쳐진
<SYNC Start=336079><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=336080><P Class=ENCC>
당신에게요, 여왕님
<SYNC Start=340316><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=340317><P Class=ENCC>
Mary: 머시
<SYNC Start=342751><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=342752><P Class=ENCC>
