<SYNC Start=345721><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=345722><P Class=ENCC>
네가 제일 불쌍해
<SYNC Start=348124><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=348125><P Class=ENCC>
